data.description: Welcome to this  3 bedroom 2 bath home located in Beaver County,Center Township. Nestled in Central Valley School District  this home features 2 first floor bedrooms, full bathroom, kitchen, and dining are. On the second floor you will find a spacious bedroom, full bathroom and plenty of storage space. Off street parking is readily available provided by a driveway and detached garage accompanying the home. Enjoy the outdoors with a fenced in backyard and patio space. On those extra sunny days relax in the shade on the enclosed back porch. This location offers nearby access to Interstate 376 for those commuting to work or traveling to the airport. 158 Stone Quarry road also finds itself near Penn State Beaver campus, Beaver Valley Mall, and the Shell Cracker Plant.
